    <div class="section">
      

<div id="review_979191782" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/979191782" />
    <a title="Jabiz Raisdana" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/12989115-jabiz-raisdana"><img alt="Jabiz Raisdana" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1566902762p2/12989115.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/979191782?book_show_action=true">Jun 27, 2014</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Jabiz Raisdana" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Jabiz Raisdana" href="/user/show/12989115-jabiz-raisdana">Jabiz Raisdana</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/12989115-jabiz-raisdana?shelf=adventure">adventure</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/12989115-jabiz-raisdana?shelf=child-labor">child-labor</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/12989115-jabiz-raisdana?shelf=childhood">childhood</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/12989115-jabiz-raisdana?shelf=war">war</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/12989115-jabiz-raisdana?shelf=afghanistan">afghanistan</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/12989115-jabiz-raisdana?shelf=violence">violence</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/12989115-jabiz-raisdana?shelf=btc">btc</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer979191782" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17503244541181674252">Another great book about the everyday heroism so many young people deal with in the face of great odds. Books like this are important to remind us that beyond the comfort of our everyday lives, people all over the world persevere beyond what we could ever imagine just to survive and be free. Well-written, this is a captivating story and another important read for students at UWCSEA and beyond. Like Never Fall Down, Boys Without Names and Little Bee, this is a book that you will not believe, but </span>
  <span id="freeText17503244541181674252" style="display:none">Another great book about the everyday heroism so many young people deal with in the face of great odds. Books like this are important to remind us that beyond the comfort of our everyday lives, people all over the world persevere beyond what we could ever imagine just to survive and be free. Well-written, this is a captivating story and another important read for students at UWCSEA and beyond. Like Never Fall Down, Boys Without Names and Little Bee, this is a book that you will not believe, but need to read. It just might make service feel that mush more real to you. </span>
  <a data-text-id="17503244541181674252" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


